n devices, and secondary surge arresters, as well as develops properties and leases land and premises. In addition, it engages in equity shares, debt instruments, and mutual funds investment activities, as well as involved in generation of power from windmill. Further, the company offers lightning arresters, discharge counter, and related accessories and services. It also exports its products. Elpro International Limited was incorporated in 1962 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}